flowchart TD
    Start([应用启动]) --> CheckUser{有用户ID?}
    CheckUser -->|是| LoadData[加载用户数据]
    CheckUser -->|否| Register[跳转注册页面]

    LoadData --> LoadPets[加载宠物列表]
    LoadPets --> LoadPosts[加载动态数据]
    LoadPosts --> LoadMilestones[加载里程碑]
    LoadMilestones --> ShowHome[显示首页]

    Register --> InputName[输入昵称]
    InputName --> InputAvatar[选择头像]
    InputAvatar --> ConfirmRegister[确认注册]
    ConfirmRegister --> CreateUser[创建User对象]
    CreateUser --> SetCurrentUser[设置当前用户]
    SetCurrentUser --> ShowHome

    ShowHome --> PetManage[宠物管理]
    ShowHome --> PostPublish[动态发布]
    ShowHome --> PostInteract[动态交互]
    ShowHome --> TimelinePage[大事年表]
    ShowHome --> AIInsights[AI看板]
    ShowHome --> SwitchUser[切换用户]

    PetManage --> CheckPets{有宠物?}
    CheckPets -->|否| EmptyPet[显示空状态]
    CheckPets -->|是| ShowPetList[显示资料卡列表]
    EmptyPet --> AddPet[点击添加宝贝]
    ShowPetList --> AddPet

    AddPet --> PetName[输入名称]
    PetName --> PetSpecies[选择种类]
    PetSpecies --> PetGender[选择性别]
    PetGender --> PetBirthday[设置生日]
    PetBirthday --> PetArrival[设置到家日期]
    PetArrival --> PetAvatar[上传头像]
    PetAvatar --> SavePet[点击保存]
    SavePet --> CreatePet[创建Pet对象]
    CreatePet --> StorePet[更新localStorage]
    StorePet --> ShowPetCard[显示资料卡]

    PostPublish --> SelectPetFilter[选择宠物筛选]
    SelectPetFilter --> InputContent[输入文字]
    InputContent --> AddImage[添加图片]
    AddImage --> CheckAIRecognize{点击AI识别?}
    CheckAIRecognize -->|是| AIService[上传AI服务]
    AIService --> AIResult[识别健康事件]
    AIResult --> CheckEvent[用户勾选事件]
    CheckEvent --> ConfirmArchive[确认归档]
    ConfirmArchive --> CreateMilestone[创建里程碑记录]
    CheckAIRecognize -->|否| ClickPublish

    CreateMilestone --> ClickPublish[点击发布]
    ClickPublish --> CreatePost[创建Post对象]
    CreatePost --> StorePost[更新localStorage]
    StorePost --> InsertPostTop[动态插入顶部]

    PostInteract --> ImagePreview[图片预览]
    PostInteract --> ToggleLike[点赞交互]
    PostInteract --> AddComment[评论发布]

    ImagePreview --> ClickImage[点击图片]
    ClickImage --> ShowPreview[显示预览弹窗]
    ShowPreview --> ClosePreview[点击关闭]

    ToggleLike --> ClickHeart[点击心形图标]
    ClickHeart --> CheckLiked{已点赞?}
    CheckLiked -->|是| TurnGray[心形变灰色]
    CheckLiked -->|否| TurnRed[心形变红色]
    TurnGray --> UpdateLocalState[更新本地状态]
    TurnRed --> UpdateLocalState
    UpdateLocalState --> UpdateStore[更新localStorage]
    UpdateStore --> ShowLikers[显示点赞者]

    AddComment --> ClickCommentBox[点击评论框]
    ClickCommentBox --> InputComment[输入评论]
    InputComment --> ClickSend[点击发送]
    ClickSend --> CreateComment[创建Comment对象]
    CreateComment --> StoreComment[更新localStorage]
    StoreComment --> ShowComment[评论显示在列表]

    TimelinePage --> SelectPetFilter2[选择宠物筛选]
    SelectPetFilter2 --> SelectTypeFilter[选择类型筛选]
    SelectTypeFilter --> FilterData[过滤里程碑数据]
    FilterData --> SortData[按日期倒序]
    SortData --> ShowTimeline[显示时间轴]

    ShowTimeline --> ClickAdd[点击+按钮]
    ClickAdd --> ShowAddModal[显示添加弹窗]
    ShowAddModal --> SelectEventType[选择事件类型]
    SelectEventType --> InputTitle[输入标题]
    InputTitle --> InputDesc[输入描述]
    InputDesc --> SelectDate[选择日期]
    SelectDate --> CheckWeight{类型是体重?}
    CheckWeight -->|是| InputWeight[输入体重数值]
    CheckWeight -->|否| SaveMilestone[点击保存]
    InputWeight --> SaveMilestone

    SaveMilestone --> CreateMilestone2[创建Milestone对象]
    CreateMilestone2 --> StoreMilestone[更新localStorage]
    StoreMilestone --> RefreshTimeline[刷新时间轴]

    AIInsights --> GetCurrentPet[获取当前宠物]
    GetCurrentPet --> CheckPetExist{有宠物?}
    CheckPetExist -->|否| ShowEmpty[显示空状态]
    CheckPetExist -->|是| FilterPetMilestones[过滤宠物里程碑]

    FilterPetMilestones --> CountEvents[统计健康事件数]
    CountEvents --> CheckEventCount{事件数>=2?}
    CheckEventCount -->|否| ShowGuide[显示引导提示]
    CheckEventCount -->|是| GenerateReport[生成健康报告]

    GenerateReport --> CalcScore[计算健康评分]
    GenerateReport --> AnalyzeWeight[分析体重趋势]
    GenerateReport --> CheckVaccine[检查疫苗状态]
    GenerateReport --> AnalyzeDeworm[分析驱虫频率]
    GenerateReport --> GenerateAdvice[生成健康建议]
    GenerateReport --> StatsSummary[统计历史摘要]
    CalcScore --> ShowReport[显示完整报告]
    AnalyzeWeight --> ShowReport
    CheckVaccine --> ShowReport
    AnalyzeDeworm --> ShowReport
    GenerateAdvice --> ShowReport
    StatsSummary --> ShowReport

    SwitchUser --> ClickAvatar[点击用户头像]
    ClickAvatar --> ShowUserList[显示用户列表]
    ShowUserList --> SelectUser[选择目标用户]
    SelectUser --> SetNewUserId[设置新currentUserId]
    SetNewUserId --> ReloadData[调用loadData]
    ReloadData --> LoadNewPets[加载新用户宠物]
    LoadNewPets --> LoadNewPosts[加载新用户动态]
    LoadNewPosts --> LoadNewMilestones[加载新用户里程碑]
    LoadNewMilestones --> UpdateStoreState[更新store状态]
    UpdateStoreState --> ShowHome

    ShowHome --> PetSync[跨页面宠物同步]
    PetSync --> SelectPet[选择宠物]
    SelectPet --> SetPetId[调用setCurrentPetId]
    SetPetId --> UpdatePetStore[更新store.currentPetId]
    UpdatePetStore --> UpdatePetStorage[更新localStorage]
    UpdatePetStorage --> SyncPages[页面同步更新]
